{"tid":2080788,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加強核威懾力　F35A戰機投擲戰術核彈照片首公開","createTime":"2020-06-26T16:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T18:51:49.000Z","uid":295230,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f174cee70c79ed1b157db6eedcafd5292b318fe4","tid":2080788,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:29:19.000Z","msg":"中美關係緊張之際，美國國防部近日首次公開測試照片，顯示F35A隱形戰機投擲B61-12型戰術核彈。除了F35A外，國防部日前亦公開F15E戰機投擲同型戰術核彈的照片。<br />\n<br />\n國防部轄下、專責研發F35不同型號戰機的F-35聯合計劃辦公室發布照片，顯示F35A打開武器艙後投擲B61-12型戰術核彈。測試於去年6月至本年4月期間舉行，由加州愛德華空軍基地第461飛行測試中隊負責，預計2023年1月取得認證。F-35A一旦通過測試，將具備發射常規武器及核武器能力，成為雙重用途戰機。<br />\n<br />\nB61-12型戰術核彈是美軍最新的延壽型核彈，將取代舊式的3、4、7及10型，可搭載在F15E、F16、F35戰機及B2轟炸機，加強美國的核威懾能力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3RQCxEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3RQCxEo.jpg&h=7bfb0f33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a94f61c5bfaa9d9949edc4014a3ddf659f068025","tid":2080788,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:31:19.000Z","msg":"🚬"},{"pid":"a77a04da0b510a5eefb22dd3b6898f483ddae46a","tid":2080788,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67a1fe584be194f92cab494f55397582e2fa33e","tid":2080788,"uid":131121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"投擲核彈個機師走唔走得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0e044d48d38ec66344d02e857a791dd78efb6e","tid":2080788,"uid":191579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e67a1fe584be194f92cab494f55397582e2fa33e","tid":2080788,"uid":131121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"投擲核彈個機師走唔走得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"放心. 番到屋企先會爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da38b548ea1cccf3057c42ccdfb21fbcb0d5d031","tid":2080788,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:33:24.000Z","msg":"美國F-15E「打擊鷹」戰鬥機在6月初已成功測試最新的B61-12延壽型戰術核彈，成為首架兼容新核彈的戰機。<br />\n<br />\n根據《國防新聞》報導，美國專門研發核武非核部分的桑迪亞國家實驗室（Sandia）表示，3月時，F-15E在內華達州的托諾帕試驗場進行了2次測試，一次大約在304.8公尺的高空，以接近音速的速度釋放模擬彈，另一次則在大約7.62公里的高空進行，2次測試均成功達成預定目標。"},{"pid":"cdf659324cc190d477e02f8d1522b4ed1f2bb86b","tid":2080788,"uid":295230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e67a1fe584be194f92cab494f55397582e2fa33e","tid":2080788,"uid":131121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"投擲核彈個機師走唔走得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"個機超音速飛走，而且戰機載既核彈破壞力無戰略核彈咁高"},{"pid":"68973ff64ba6f65975b686e058a79af29f9a331c","tid":2080788,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e67a1fe584be194f92cab494f55397582e2fa33e","tid":2080788,"uid":131121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"投擲核彈個機師走唔走得切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"唔係傳統核彈,炸地底設施用"},{"pid":"7cd71ebce5f4c157d423a3e93f9f4bd063380feb","tid":2080788,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3461c67c3d470977efd093e24ea9ab2e01d93cd7","tid":2080788,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68973ff64ba6f65975b686e058a79af29f9a331c","tid":2080788,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e67a1fe584be194f92cab494f55397582e2fa33e",